author: {'steamid': '76561198144995826', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 2, 'playtime_forever': 882, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 232, 'playtime_at_review': 777, 'last_played': 1711618930}
review:
總體來說是款好遊戲
某些關卡設計得很有戰術性

舉個例子
Area 9800戰役第一關和Tilarus-5戰役第四關
前者只是一堆異形衝過來啃你，大量火力就可以應對了
但後者在前者的基礎下，多了兩隻盾蟲
讓你對付大量異形外，還得防盾蟲的單下高傷害
最後是靠機槍塔+電圈+MTD6處理掉的
這導致每個關卡都要特別進去看一下敵人的配置
以免你等級過低，可發揮的戰術選擇過於稀少
建議在挑戰那些比較困難的關卡前，先練到滿等

對了，升級軍銜只是為了炫耀用的，他不會增加你任何能力數值之類的東西
而且升級後等級歸零，能使用的裝備也回到最初的狀態，要重新練等解鎖
不是特別在意軍銜的話，建議練到滿等就好

author: {'steamid': '76561198256941240', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 16, 'playtime_forever': 1504, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1504, 'last_played': 1710581552}
review:
看到官方还在更新又回来玩了玩。首先，不得不说这游戏人是真少，一下午就那几个人，连老外都顶着几百ping来玩。
再说说游戏吧，这游戏还是有点意思的，面对汹涌的虫子，让大佬带个榴弹一路冲冲冲才是真谛。作为一个以前被大佬带过几次的任务的菜鸡，现在回来玩已经完全记不得路线了，只会用喷火器乱烧，然后拿着榴弹炸到自己。另外，有时候真想让ai拿枪，他打的都比我准哈哈哈。
总之，作为一款免费游戏，内容也称得上丰富，也有很多技巧和套路可以研究练习。
最后大佬们都很友好，还没见到什么小圈子的妖魔鬼怪。然后，HELLDIVERS 2是真贵，再去玩玩深岩银河吧。

author: {'steamid': '76561198008886808', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 4, 'playtime_forever': 459, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 4, 'playtime_at_review': 455, 'last_played': 1712064211}
review:
Дисклеймер: Я НЕ фанат игры! могу в тонкостях ошибаться, ( это для фанатов) если ваше мнение отличается от моего, прошу написать, коментарий (будет приятно почитать).
Описание: Фантастический top-down шутер, для прохождения как одному (с ботами или без), так и командой до восьми человек (что в разы интересней).
Игровой процесс: Главной целью, а также игровым процессом и сюжетом, является борьба с инопланетными жуками (и выполнением разнообразных заданий), на территориях научных, военных и прочих баз. Эти жуки наступают огромными 
ордами, делая игру похожей на ALIEN SHOOTER.
Сюжет: Главными героями являются морпехи, посланные для Зачистки колоний людей от инопланетного супостата (жуков то есть). Наши герои делятся на четыре класса (см. ниже"Классы"). Прилетая на планеты они выполняют задания,(Уничтожение лечинок жуков, заваривание шлюзов и тд.) с последующей эвакуацией.
Классы:
1.Сержант. Руководит всем отрядом расставляя точки приоритета на карте (для игры нужно быть немного стратегом).
2.Пулемётчик. Очень важный боец, прикрывающий всех шквальным огнём крупнокалиберного пулемёта (играть за него легче всего).
3.Медик. Лечит остальных бойцов (спасибо, капитан очевидность).
4.Техник. Боец выполняющий технические задачи(взлом кодовых замков, заваривание гермодверей и установка турелей). зачастую необходимый для выполнения задания. Играя за него, для выполнения некоторых задач, например для вскрытия замков, необходимо играть в мини-игры.
Стиль: Антураж Игры напоминает стары SCi-FI фильмы. архитектура комплексов, как в Чужом, а дизайн жуков почти как в Звёздном Десанте.
Итак- переходим к самому отзыву.
Достоинства:
1. Качество! Проработка локаций, врагов и предметов на высшем уровне!
2. Игра бесплатная! Доступна любому желающему, возможно за исключением некоторых предметов (точно не знаю).
3. Системные требования (они достаточно низкие).
4. Интересный геймплей. Игра бросает вызов, но бояться играть не стоит, так как сложность гибко настраивается. 
5. Разнообразие кампаний, локаций и врагов! От базовых, опасаться которых нужно лишь при большом количестве, до огромных и сильных, которые легко могут ранить и даже убить игрока.
6. Активный многопользовательский режим и сообщество. На серверах всегда есть игроки, а сообщество создаёт множество кампаний, карт и модов.
Недостатки: Я не заметил.

author: {'steamid': '76561198007845342', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 370, 'playtime_forever': 84, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 84, 'last_played': 1709601652}
review:
A decent multiplayer focused top-down shooter made by Valve/Steam. Also it is FREE.

Recently I tried Helldivers 1 and the gameplay reminded me of Alien Swarm.
I have a weird relationship with this game, have reinstalled it countless times, but never could really get into it.

The game explains very little while throwing you head first into combat where you have to grind for better gear and weapons. Wouldn't be as bad if not for the brain dead team that can't survive past the 1st stage of level 1!

It is simply not my jam, but I can see what fun can be had in this.

Overall a nice concept that has been built upon and spawned games such as Synthetik and Ruiner.
Also this Reactive Drop reboot is much MUCH better than the barren 2010 game.

review: Jogo barato e bom, ainda tem oficina (Jogando a campanha original ainda tem outros mapas que voce baixa e joga). Tem alguns servidores públicos que tem ping alto. Mas você entra nem sente que ta com ping alto você consegue jogar tranquilo com os outros. Melhor ainda quando se tem amigos que vocês planejam as estratégias e podem passar a fase tranquilo. 5 Classes com duas variações cada uma é importante (A técnico é essencial para todas e esse não pode morrer). As armas você vai desbloqueando conforme os níveis. O jogo não é difícil de entender, conforme você vai jogando os botões que você tem que usar mostram na tela. E quanto mais joga você descobre mais dele. Não é enjoativo e facilmente você passa um bom tempo nele. recomendo!

author: {'steamid': '76561199208403421', 'num_games_owned': 31, 'num_reviews': 20, 'playtime_forever': 104, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 104, 'last_played': 1701042330}
review:
Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop - Intense Cooperative Mayhem

Rating: ★★★★☆

Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop, an expansive and intense cooperative top-down shooter developed by Reactive Drop Team, delivers a thrilling experience that captures the essence of teamwork and survival against overwhelming extraterrestrial threats. Originally inspired by a Source Engine mod, Reactive Drop enhances the formula, offering an impressive array of content for fans of cooperative gameplay.

The gameplay centers around a squad of marines tasked with completing a variety of missions on infested space colonies. The top-down perspective provides a unique vantage point, fostering strategic planning and coordination as players face waves of relentless alien enemies. The variety of available classes, each with distinct roles and abilities, encourages diverse team compositions and strategic depth.

The game truly shines in its cooperative multiplayer mode, where up to eight players can join forces to battle the alien hordes. Communication and teamwork are paramount, as players must coordinate their movements, cover each other, and utilize their unique skills to overcome challenging scenarios. The sense of camaraderie and accomplishment after successfully completing a mission with a well-coordinated team is one of Reactive Drop's most rewarding aspects.

Reactive Drop boasts a robust selection of weapons and equipment, providing players with ample options to tailor their loadouts to suit their preferred playstyles. The progression system, though not overly complex, offers a sense of accomplishment as players unlock new gear and abilities through successful missions.

Visually, Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop may not boast cutting-edge graphics, but its atmospheric lighting and detailed environments contribute to an immersive and suspenseful atmosphere. The alien designs are diverse and menacing, adding to the intensity of the firefights.

One notable aspect is the extensive modding community surrounding Reactive Drop, which has contributed additional content, missions, and features. This dedication from the community has significantly extended the game's longevity, providing players with a continuous stream of new challenges and experiences.

While Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop offers a rich cooperative experience, it may feel less engaging in single-player mode, as the game is clearly designed with multiplayer in mind. Additionally, the learning curve for newcomers can be steep, and the absence of a comprehensive tutorial may leave some players feeling a bit overwhelmed initially.

In conclusion, Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop is a gem for fans of cooperative shooters, offering an adrenaline-pumping, alien-blasting experience that rewards teamwork and strategy. With a thriving modding community, diverse gameplay elements, and a wealth of content, Reactive Drop continues to be a standout title for those seeking an intense and challenging cooperative gaming experience.

author: {'steamid': '76561199027163658', 'num_games_owned': 76, 'num_reviews': 8, 'playtime_forever': 16337, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 1, 'playtime_at_review': 16337, 'last_played': 1712407327}
review:
前几天全成就了，玩了四年的游戏，想说电视嗯么，游戏是好游戏，就是官方不知道在想啥，一开始更新都是增加中文和趣味的提示语，比如击杀队友会有个干得漂亮，现在更新就是改UI，上次的大更新就是改了UI跟腻码二次元网游一样，吐了，我更新完第一次进甚至不知道怎么找房间，还有房间列表也是改成答辩。当然了也谢谢官方一直免费更新地图，偶尔打开带带萌新还是挺好的，就是有的猛新不听还犟，那只能祝你好似。     至今难忘当时无意间发现的地图bug到现在还没修，挺有意思的，美好的回忆

所有新人 所有！进游戏之后，esc 选项 高级设置 一直往右选杂项，把那个死亡镜头给关了！

给我点个赞吧孩子想要点数

Played a bit when TF2 was at the height of its popularity, absolute unbelievable a free product of such excellent quality is still being supported more than a decade later. Everyone who has Steam and enjoyed the Alien franchise should play this game.

author: {'steamid': '76561198018182447', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 2, 'playtime_forever': 874, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 799, 'last_played': 1708984214}
review:
Jako fan oryginalnego Alien Swarma mogę z czystym sumieniem polecić Reactive Drop. Wszystko, co lubimy z oryginału, zostało powielone w ulepszonej i bardziej rozwiniętej formie. 

W Reactive Drop mamy więc szereg nowych misji i kampanii, możliwość zwiększenia stanu osobowego drużyny do 8 graczy, nowe wyzwania oraz tryby gry. Wszystko, czego brakowało w pierwowzorze! 

Mechanika pozostaje taka sama - jest to wciąż wielce angażujący shooter izometryczny. Gra wieloosobowa daje wiele frajdy, szczególnie grając ze znajomymi. Otoczka audiowizualna, mimo upływu lat, wciąż trzyma się znakomicie. Jestem pełen podziwu, że ta gra jest darmowa. Zdecydowanie jeden z lepszych darmowych tytułów dostępnych na Steam.

author: {'steamid': '76561198066614128', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 10, 'playtime_forever': 1228, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1228, 'last_played': 1707232933}
review:
Great game that remind me to an old game that I used to play: alien shooter.

This a fun game to try with friend if you like co op shooting game. Could be hard for some new player, so don't hesitate or ashamed to try the easy difficulty first. 

One of the best co op shooting game in my opinion. And beside of that, Alien Swarm is completely FREE. So, if you don't like it you can just go uninstall it. At least try this game once with some of your friend. Maybe you gonna like it.

I think one thing that should be really appreciated is that the developers really care with this game. They update this game regularly, 7 years after this free game got released! They even drop a massive update not long time ago. Thanks, devs!

author: {'steamid': '76561199516299746', 'num_games_owned': 11, 'num_reviews': 5, 'playtime_forever': 2415, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 2415, 'last_played': 1706032003}
review:
10/10
I'm known to have long and in depth reviews but I will just say:
if you really want a some action packed game that offers you top-down, third and firs person shooting experiences and cooperative team effort, and being easy to play but hard to master THEN THIS IS YOUR GAME!
*plus the game has a nice workshop/modding community <3


Game properties:
💰Price tag\\
-FREE!

📖Story & Writing\\
-Good, there is always lore bits to explore in each chapter

🖼Graphics\\
-Fine and decent

🖥Needed Specs\\
-Low and not needy!

🎮Gameplay\\
-Exciting and satisfying when making it out of close call encounter with a huge swarm

🔈Audio\\
-Perfect! (plus each character has their own voice lines being used at the right time in situational manner)

⚠️Difficulty level\\
-Balanced (but there is always more challenges to make it hard)!

🏆Progress to grind\\
-pretty easy, but with each promotion, you get back to level-1 and you start the grind again

⏳Game time\\
-Expandable, there is always more content :D

🪲Bugs & Patches\\
-Bugs are rare to find, and updates are frequently delivered

👥Fandom\\
-Epic, mostly nice and supportive

author: {'steamid': '76561197989876324', 'num_games_owned': 40, 'num_reviews': 9, 'playtime_forever': 254891, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 95, 'playtime_at_review': 251980, 'last_played': 1712077147}
review:
良心免费的休闲好游戏，没有皮肤党，没有舔狗结婚党，没有VIP充值党，外挂也很少。很适合长期玩，休闲、极限、装逼、技巧、谩骂、看戏、逗比样样具备，是为数不多的相对自由平等的游戏。
免费、不吃电脑机能、能较流畅联机、玩家没充值没特权、外挂没利润也看不上的小众游戏，试问这样的游戏还有哪里去找？市场上几乎见不到不为金钱和利益，纯粹因为爱玩游戏而运营的游戏了，此款实为宝藏级休闲小游戏了。

author: {'steamid': '76561197965047060', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 43, 'playtime_forever': 36, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 36, 'last_played': 1705495408}
review: Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop delivers an exceptional co-op multiplayer experience with intense action and strategic teamwork. The game features diverse maps, challenging missions, and a variety of alien enemies, creating an immersive atmosphere. With the addition of Reactive Drop, the game offers even more content and variety. Cooperative gameplay encourages communication and coordination, while diverse classes add strategic depth. Impressive graphics, sound design, and support from the modding community enhance the overall experience. In summary, Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop is a highly recommended, replayable game for fans of cooperative shooters.

author: {'steamid': '76561199352236073', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 1, 'playtime_forever': 8324, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 3769, 'last_played': 1711252060}
review:
这款多人单人都可以游玩的游戏，拥有第一人称，第三人称，上帝视角3个视角模式，你可以在创意工坊里面添加收藏自己喜欢的mod来进行游戏模型、音乐、界面、武器等等多个方面的修改~~~也包括一些练习用的挑战摸着，一些类似于外挂般的辅助功能等等~~还可以自己开启个人服务器游玩.......
    
    作为一名新手玩家一开始我也是单纯当做射击，火力压制类打击感游戏来体验，但不是------一开始最好是先与自己的一些小伙伴一起以“困难”难度开始通关，熟悉异形的出生点以及攻击特点，慢慢开始适应再调整为跟高难度。往往玩到中期人数不够4人的情况下，高残酷难度稍微落单就可能暴毙，往往一关需要看攻略打很多次，这也是一个过渡期，因为大多数玩家可能在某一关卡住就会逐渐觉得枯燥，于是渐渐放弃了这款游戏，因为我的朋友也是如此，关卡都没全部打通，就只剩我一个人玩了。我就自己带3名Ai，分别操控继续通关征途。。。。也是偶然间发现了一些大佬们各种单通过关才知道------这款游戏不单单是火力点，包括走位、反应、弹道、速通等多方面的技巧才是我们真正需要练习，但是这段量变引起质变的路程十分的艰难！！！等你能够做到一个就是一只小队的时候，只靠一名角色就能随意穿梭在异形中，杀出虫围、华丽的单通solo关卡，我相信你也不会有遗憾了！

review:
初期装備が汎用、容量と要求スペックちゃっちいので誰でもすぐつけて遊べます
加え人数制限がほぼなく（８枠）、システムがシンプルで遊びやすい、lethal company枠のひまつぶしゲームです

ワークショップ対応なのでMODは絶対に遊ぶように　大陸のオタクが日夜大量のブルーアーカイブMODをアップしてておもろい　探してもヌード系はなかったです　働けや

それはそうと直近のアプデで初期スキンの一部が残り、スキンMODが実質機能しなくなるバグがあります
キーボード設定からコンソールの割り当てを確認、該当ボタンを押してコンソールが出たらrd_marine_gear 0を入力すると治ります　掲示板の外人ニキありがとう　名前は忘れた　ごめん（笑）

感謝の気持ちはアワードでお願いします

author: {'steamid': '76561199424762672', 'num_games_owned': 34, 'num_reviews': 36, 'playtime_forever': 6206, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 5526, 'last_played': 1704729397}
review:
Reseña de Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop: Una Intensa Experiencia Cooperativa de Combate

Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop, desarrollado por Black Cat Games y lanzado en 2017, es un juego de disparos en tercera persona de ciencia ficción que se destaca por su enfoque en la cooperación entre jugadores. Inspirado en el juego original Alien Swarm y basado en el motor Source de Valve, Reactive Drop ofrece una experiencia intensa y táctica.

Acción Cooperativa:
La esencia de Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop radica en su enfoque en la cooperación. Los jugadores forman un equipo de hasta ocho personas, cada una con habilidades y roles únicos. La comunicación y la coordinación son esenciales para superar las hordas de alienígenas y completar los objetivos de las misiones.

Variedad de Clases y Equipamiento:
El juego presenta varias clases, cada una con habilidades específicas, lo que fomenta la especialización y la colaboración. Además, el amplio arsenal de armas y equipo permite a los jugadores adaptarse a diferentes situaciones y enemigos. La elección inteligente del equipo antes de cada misión agrega una capa estratégica al juego.

Desafíos Tácticos y Misiones:
Las misiones en Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop ofrecen una variedad de objetivos, desde escoltar cargas hasta infiltrarse en instalaciones alienígenas. La inteligencia artificial de los enemigos requiere estrategias específicas, y la dificultad aumenta a medida que avanzas, proporcionando un desafío continuo y gratificante.

Gráficos y Ambiente:
Aunque no destaca por gráficos de última generación, Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop ofrece un ambiente tenso y claustrofóbico. Los niveles están diseñados con atención al detalle, y los efectos visuales contribuyen a la atmósfera tensa del juego.

Comunidad y Mods:
Una de las fortalezas de Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop es su comunidad activa y la compatibilidad con mods. Los jugadores pueden crear y disfrutar de contenido adicional, lo que amplía la vida útil del juego y brinda nuevas experiencias.

Interfaz de Usuario y Controles:
La interfaz de usuario es intuitiva y fácil de entender, lo que facilita la inmersión en el juego. Los controles son sólidos, permitiendo una experiencia fluida y precisa durante las intensas secuencias de combate.

Conclusión:
Alien Swarm: Reactive Drop ofrece una experiencia cooperativa única y desafiante, destacando por su énfasis en la estrategia y la colaboración. Aunque puede carecer de los gráficos más avanzados, su fortaleza radica en la jugabilidad táctica y en la posibilidad de disfrutar de misiones dinámicas con amigos. La activa comunidad y la compatibilidad con mods garantizan que Reactive Drop continúe siendo una opción atractiva para los amantes de los juegos cooperativos.

author: {'steamid': '76561198097740199', 'num_games_owned': 266, 'num_reviews': 76, 'playtime_forever': 1256, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1225, 'last_played': 1703378986}
review:
Writing a review on a free game? Yeah
Is it worth it? Oh every cent bud 

on a serious note I am having a lot of fun with AS:RD, especially the third person mode - even if some of the maps are clearly not made to be viewed from that angle lol. I have very few complaints about this game overall, and even when I die to the swarm I got no one to blame but myself. Weapon types are a lot of fun even if some are slight variants of each other - they have enough about them to stand unique and can really change how you handle a fight. 

Again, its a free game, I am writing this however to warn people to not play one of the campaigns as it uh, well, it just sucks.

"Reduction" is absolute dogwater in every. single. aspect. and you should avoid it. Play any of the others. Play them again, and then a third time and you'll love it. 

The slog to get to the final mission of reduction and the the constant repeats I have attempted to finish it just ruined the mood.

author: {'steamid': '76561198867244476', 'num_games_owned': 6, 'num_reviews': 13, 'playtime_forever': 216, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 11, 'last_played': 1702824318}
review:
1.当你被虫群围困的时候，不要惊慌，试着做几个反击动作，然后你会死得优雅一些。
2.当你的小伙伴还剩最后几滴血并被虫群围攻时，试着帮忙补上几枪，让你的小伙伴有尊严地牺牲。
3.当你被虫子骑脸并持续中毒时，请尝试大声吟唱ギリギリ愛以毒攻毒。
4.当你遇到大型异虫而不知所措时，不要肛正面，尝试用瞎JB乱滚的方法眩晕它。
5.当你打了肾上腺素并进入子弹时间时，请跟着放慢语速，然后解锁MDZZ成就。
6.进攻的路上太无聊？推荐用火焰喷射器点燃队友，然后欣赏他们的娇喘。
7.与虫群战斗时最危险的位置永运是队友的前面。
8.当你与队友走散而落单时，尝试在右下角的小地图上寻找他们，死亡的机率便会由90％下降到89.5％。
9.卡关的时候要仔细分析小队的战术是否有漏洞，并制定新的战术。然而你会发现瞎JB乱打才是真理。
10.以上，祝你游戏愉快（笑）。

review: Super underrated. It's a blast to play (especially with friends) and it has a really interesting world and art style. This game is also insanely stressful but in a good way. The amount of times I have been screaming my head off and clenching my asshole is enough to fill a book. There's also a lot of customization and modularity to your playstyle. It's cool, it's scary, it's varied, and most of all; it's fun. Get 3 people to play this with you and you'll have a good time.

author: {'steamid': '76561198298031621', 'num_games_owned': 168, 'num_reviews': 201, 'playtime_forever': 153, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 82, 'last_played': 1702076906}
review:
I first played this game 4 years ago and although I couldn't convince my firends to play, I still found it to be a great experience.

I re-downloaded it and IT IS STILL GETTING UPDATES!??!!?
-visuals are awesome
-guns feel powerful
-solo controls of the friendly AI are very nice
-you can re-watch your games? cool.
-music is on point
-sounds of everything is honestly great

We do not deserve this game for free.
